% /filter {

% } def


% Set the page size
72 72 scale
300 500 translate

% Define colors
/DarkGray { 0.2 0.2 0.2 setrgbcolor } def
/White { 1 1 1 setrgbcolor } def
/Orange { 1 0.5 0 setrgbcolor } def

% Draw the body of the snowman
White
300 100 40 0 360 arc
fill
300 240 60 0 360 arc
fill
300 360 80 0 360 arc
fill

% Draw the eyes
DarkGray
260 375 5 0 360 arc
fill
340 375 5 0 360 arc
fill

% Draw the mouth
0.05 setlinewidth
300 355 20 0 180 arc
stroke

% Draw the nose
Orange
300 385 5 0 360 arc
fill

% Draw the arms
2 setlinewidth
270 310 250 0 45 arc
stroke
330 310 250 135 180 arc
stroke

% Draw the hat
DarkGray
240 420 120 0 180 arc
fill
240 420 20 0 360 arc
fill
360 420 20 0 360 arc
fill
220 420 40 0 360 arc
fill
380 420 40 0 360 arc
fill

% Show the result
showpage
You can copy and paste this code into a PostScript interpreter or editor to view and modify the snowman as needed.




